isited and Following up meeting with Suchitra regarding the deal update and regarding the payment terms why it is necessary and important for 100% payment updates for the InBody 120 and updated me after discussion that needs time to connect with the source . payment information about it and will update me that already that why InBody is must in the current scenario.

VLCC for 2 New Project of Elite Centres for Introduction of High End Models and Also  Some Issue were there for pending payments So Meeting is Scheduled on Monday for the same

Meeting with Mr. Dinesh virtually for forwarding of the balance payment of RS. 200000 for dispatching of machine IB270 at their gym center sir has requested for time till coming Monday for the same awaiting his call

Installation of Demo machine of IB270 and update of the use at their gym as sir requires the machine for pre sales activities we have given them a demo model till Monday for soft launch and will be closing the deal with forwarding 100% payment by Tuesday to close for either IB120 or IB270 will be visiting to the center on Monday for training too
InBody120 finalized via bangalore dealer because of Cash Transaction from Client. They are doing transaction By Monday with 100% payment for IB120.

Going to Meet Dr. Narayan Acharya Physiotherapist at Dwarka hospital going to discuss importance of BCA at their hospital and uses in their application met the doctor and explained about how internal parameters of skeletal muscle mass is related to body balance and body structure for strength and ability sir like the machine but they have a very low budget has suggested for buying the machine by January 2021

Meeting Virtually with prem manager of fit day Pvt LTD operations for update on advance payment on IB120 of 50% for their second order client has said he will share the UTR number for cross checking of the payment received will be receiving the same and forwarding it to our finance team for confirmation

This was a virtual meeting, which was scheduled for closing with Franchisee fitness Tone fitness with Mr. Karan on call we were in negotiations with Mr. Hanumath owner of the franchise but unfortunately sir was stressing on part payments for few months which wasn't possible from our side hence conveyed the possible part payments option from our side now waiting for the client to update back
New Order has been closed for his new Opened centre of Suppliments. Now Also Tied up with him for InBody Dial thats why Gave him Combo deal with Dial and IB120 and Finalized the same.

Co-ordinating with Mr. Amjad club manager of Flip Body for Update on the order of IB270 for their gym as I had requested sir for advance payment of 60% and the remaining amount PDC's sir has said that they are into managing their funds and will update me back on 15th of December
We did 270 demo with the owner, however looking after budget, we also pitched 120. Payment terms denied, also he didn't look much eager to invest

The meeting was about police academy tender, I AM doing one chattisgarh police academy tender with Karn Sharma and requested Onyx to support as a bidder for this tender. Shared the document list and other requirements

Final meeting with Mr. Sachin. Deal closed. Payment terms decided. Advance payment will be done by Friday.

column3: New Meeting with the Chairman Dr.P.S.Pillai
column12: I had a meeting with Dr.Pillai and he really liked the product which is InBody 770 and even his management liked it the most. Now we had a discussion how this can be taken forward . Some of the management people liked to invest on machines and some like trying put in such a way that they wanted to get the machine for cheaper rental . I have tried to showcase how this machine can play a vital role in a school after this pandemic as parents of your student will defenitely satisfy after seeing that the school is taking care of their children's health, that will create a good brand value and name in the market. with the help of this machine new admission can also increase as when parents come with their kids will see how a school caters both the health as well as the education a vital parts. Also try to understand the number of obese students in the school. how a health monitoring device can be helpful to make them motivate to be fit. After all this discussion Dr.Pillai asked that he will then have a discussion with the board and again will meet and will discuss further with me.

Today we had a detailed discussion regarding InBody 270 and InBody120.  Had a discussion what are the advantages of InBody 270 compare to InBody 120 for his clinic. Then regarding pricing, we were talking about. So I gave an offer saying an opening year an Offer for both the machine. After that, we had a detailed discussion what are the service issue that basically arises and how much time is required and I also shared some of the cases where clients have got benefited both in terms of sales, patient satisfaction, and name. After a detailed discussion, about machine maintenance, etc he asked to share the final price quotation and he will take it to his CA and then he will finalize the order.

Today we had a discussion with Mr.Bhanudas and his 4 partners again regarding the final pricing as 4 of the partners asking price was between n 1lakh -1.4lakhs for both the InBody machines (IB120 & 270) and they were sharing some of the local company names . So I have asked them to definitely take a demo of both the machines InBody as well as the local products side by side and then he can take the decision, as because as InBody is not competing with such local brands anyway but for the satisfaction level if they want they can do it , Then also I shared two cases from pune who had faces issues using local products and fortunately, both the client have a similar link / know the other two clients very well .

After this all meeting and after sometime I again had a detail word with Mr.Bhanudas and as per him, they are now ready for the InBody as they got feedback from other gyms/their peers.

Mr.Avishek has came up with new gym set up and we had a discussion regarding about our machines and how it's going to help him for his new gym sales push and how InBody can help him to achieve that . After the detailed discussion sharing some of the reference cases and some important bodies who are using our machine and how they have got benefited then he wants to arrange a demo and he wants to see how it works and also he wants his clients reaction for the same and then he will decide whether he wants to invest such huge amount or not. So now I will be arranging one demo for him .

It was a meeting regarding the pricing of the machine and also do we have any finance option then we had a discussion regarding the different models' differences etc and then regarding the pricing negotiation. We had a long detailed discussion regarding the price, machine differences, comparison with competitors, why InBody, How many are using in Pune? Why no EMI option? Then competitors and us discussion. He was asking for EMI options for which I have mentioned the true thing that sir as per company policy we can't give any emi option, Then he asked that if a gym equipment dealer can give why cant you guys cant give it- For this, I have told that sir that's true that equipment dealers do give EMI options because it's a high budget set up is involved where paying 1cr any company can or should have a emi options, our is not in that price category, But sir still I can give you a option of using credit card with 2% interest rate if you are willing to do that sir I'm ready to accept the same but for me sir my responsibility is not only sale sir, with sale sir I focused on client efficiency and satisfaction so for that if eventually, you have to pay the whole amount then why to pay 2% extra for the same, you can pay the full amount on cheque and that 2% you can sir used it for other gym setups or day to day expenses. Then Mr.Pankaj was saying that yes I'm convinced with the InBody machine but still then your competitor is giving so much of discount and I'm getting the machine of same kind for 3 lakhs and you are charging more than 4 lakhs, So I gave a example of Apple and realme Phone (as that only came into my mind) sir realme main aim is to sale  more with bigger discount compromising on the quality and service where as apple focus on niche market , and you will see very less discounts on such products, so sir We as InBody do not compare ourself with any one in the market as we believe we are premium and we cater only premium clients like you sir. We are not any distributor who sales 'n' number of different products in the market our only focus is to give our clients the best machine, But still sir you requested for a discount I will definitely give you the same if you confirm your order by two days. After that sir is up to you sir whether you want to go with a renowned company with better service and only one-time payment or sir you want to go with a dealer who will sale X machine today then next year onwards he can start Y machines that will eventually affect the service and the cost of service, regular services etc will go high. Then he started sharing some of his experiences where he faces issue with some services related AC, Washin Machine, Then his earlier gym equipment etc. After that we had discussion the differences between InBody 270 InBody 370s then InBody 570 s, then there was again a price negotiation between InBody 270,IB370S&InBody 570s. Meanwhile he told that the competitors have also quoted through whatsapp that he will give below 3 lakhs So lastly i told sir in your areas nearby small gyms are using such machines and there are lot of variances are there , but sir If you use the 99% accuracy machine you will have a cutting edge and also you can pull those crowds towards your gym. So the investment over the machine can be recover within 4 months and also after our training it will help you even to close leads using InBody. Then as per my understanding, he was positive and then we had another discussion wat can be done with the machine or as general . At the end he said that ok will go for InBody , so share the final prices will check with the CA regarding the payment (like from which account, or credit card can be used or not) will pay the amount.

Its Discussion was more on Can they pay partially on the order, Why we do not take partial payments, Why no EMI options? . I was more talking over the status of the order why it's taking such time regarding payment for the same. But as per the above questions I have asked that sir every company has its own policy and they work on that basis. Sir Like example- In your gym if somebody takes 6 month membership and say sir that he will give the whole payment in 12 installment can it be possible sir, Lot of things are involved for the same. In terms of emi or tie ups with bank sir as you know bank do not give credits or loan to gyms so it's also hard for us to get bank loans emi from nationalized banks, So he agreed on the same and said yes that true and also they have faced the same while the setup. Then they started saying that there was a lot of expenses at the setup please give take a Pd Cheque and finalize the order, But I said sir its not possible but sir I have a 'Monday offer for you ' that if you finalized by today I will give you a flat discount of 15k from the final price and will deliver the machine by 4 days and from 1year Warranty I will give 3 years warranty with training. Then he started asking for 70k thousand discount and then 5 years of warranty, Which I did not agree on that , then he said of then will ask the partners to take a decision and finalize the order with payment. Even  just as an urgency I have just told that sir the prices can change from the next month as you know because of all the expenses have gone on the higher prices around the world. He agreed on the same.

This time Mr.Reddy bought some close friend and finance guy to understand the payment options . Then we discussed about the pricing and then I told that very few clinics are using InBody 270 so it will definitely give you and edge as both lookwise and performance wise. Then they were also discussing among them that whether its worth paying 4.5 lakhs for BCA machine. Then I asked them that sir when someone visits your clinic he will only leave with prescription but when you used this machine he will leave your clinic with his whole body insideout condition, don't you think that person when he goes back home will check the result sheet and then goes online and check for more and when he sees and understand more sir don't you think he may consult you more and not only him he will even ask his or her family member to do the same test done as certain rate as this test is not harmful. This will always increase the conversion rates of your clinic. Even its easier for you to conduct company events and etc as its not possible to carry your clinic set up but when you are getting the opportunity to carry a mini clinic with you sir Then I think sir investing 4.5 lakhs will be worth because that 4.5 laksh will pay off in no matter time.

So we were discussing about  the InBody prices compare to other machines, then discuss about which are the institutes and gyms are using InBody machine, How it was better than other brand. But then the final thing came which is why is it so costly compare to others. I told him sir if you want to buy a luxury car sir you will go directly to a BMW showroom not a Maruti showroom because the brand name itself speaks about its performance , build quality specs ,efficiency and it justifies the price that it quotes. So in BCA market we are like the same , we are not competing with some local company our machine are only used by the premium clients like you who understand or want to know or who wanted to give better, efficient and accurate result and also give importance to make changes in their clients healthcare. I believe sir you are among those premium clients who wanted to invest in quality not on quantity ? Then his answer was yes I know about InBody performance and its much better than other machines. Then we entered into the conversation of sharing some of the case studies, institutes using it , advantages of associating with us. After all discussion he said that ok please share the final quote with me so that I can place the order by end of next week . Now my job is to engage with him on regular basis with sharing whatsapp messages, calling etc.

And then he said that's great let's arrange the machine lets see how accurate are you or how good is your conviction power. Then I said sure sir I will be arranging one machine as soon as possible. had a discussion with the chairman Dr.Pillai regarding the Pricing of the machine. He was more into getting into business with us through reference sales or like getting a certain commission by selling it to different hotels ,schools etc and end of it he wants the machine for free. So I have asked that that is will be really great but even that can be more fruitefull and beneficial if he is using the machine at that time as others will see that you are the users of the machine and how you are getting benefits from it . So he said yes that is also true but indirectly again he was trying to convinced me of giving it for free. So I told him sir lets do one things sir first you invest 4.5 lakhs and within 6 months from your reference you can make 5 lakhs which is 4.5 lakhs is waived off & the machine is eventually free for you and a profit of 50k is also there. he was like ok and he asked that he will have a word with the principal and the board and then will discuss further for the same.

we had a long discussion regarding the pricing, comparing with competitors, users advantages & disadvantages of using other brands, etc. He was talking about that his friend has taken acuniq at a very cheaper rate and also they are giving 12 months emi but where as we are selling at higher cost no emi optios why should I go for it. So I asked sir while spending lakhs of rupees for buying and equipemet would you like to face issue post sales from the machine as well as from your clients if its yes sir then sir you can go ahead with the other brands. Sir do you want the results to be inaccurate and effect the lives of your client by giving wrong training or guidance if yes sir then sir other brands would be good for you . Sir do you want to associated with a brand / company or just a dealer who sales n number of products whose main aim is to do sales whereas for us its service our client. Sir most of the big clients you will see use our machine starting from NIN Institute , Big Gyms, Hospitals etc, why sir because they believe in quality , output and I'm pretty much sure sir with the status of your you also value the same that's the reason sir you are using apple phone rather than realme or oppo. Yes we do not have the options of 12 month emi but sir you can pay the amount from your credit card and convert into emis  sir. And sir the emis that the dealers are giving are mostly through bajaj finserv which processing fees are high and also interest rate and at the end sir you are paying more than the invoice value. He was then convinced as per his tone pf voice then I shared some more case studies and then we had a more discussion about general things and lastly we came into final discussion of closing the deal at 4.22lakhs and he said that he will confirm the payment in some days. now ,my job is to keep on engaging, calling and follow up.

Discussion regarding the InBody machine, who all are using, comparison between our machine and other brands . He insisted to give the machine at 1 lakh rupees but I have explained him sir if you are investing 1 lakh for a Local BCA machine and you are not getting any accurate result  then y ar you investing in such . So he told that it will just for showcase it wn't play any vital role in terms of sales or retention of their clients. So I gave a small example :- Sir In colleges or school we spent time to study , energy etc and at the end of the year we give exam and when the results are out it decides our decision for which courses, or which college or which school or even which line to choose because we know that the results which are out are authentic and it decides our future, this results might not be effective for a long run but it definitely plays a vital role directly or indirectly in our decision making process. Any Numbers when you start showing to clients they will understand the difference how much they are changing and then only they will decide to extend the membership and if the results keep on changing every day or week it will definitely affect your client's psychology and directly it will effect your business. After this then he only suddenly started sharing the same such incident. At the end he said that he will have a word with his partner and then he will see how the funds can be arranged and then he can go ahead with the same.
